                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="relax-section">
                <div class="relax">
                    <h3 class="relax-heading">Relax!</h3>
                    <p class="relax-text">We got you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stress-free">
                <p class="unwind">Feel like Unwinding?</p>
                <p class="refresh">Life can take a toll on us sometimes. A good story can be a way to reduce stress and anxiety. 
                    We'd love to make you feel refreshed!
                </p>
